These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, teacher, lawyer, engineer, dancer, nurse
There are 7 different nationalities: german, british, indonesian, dutch, malaysian, italian, brazilian
 1. the lawyer is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the malaysian is the lawyer##1
 3. the nurse is on the right of the dancer##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the italian##1
 5. the teacher is in the middle##1
 6. the german is on the far left##1
 7. the engineer is the german##1
 8. the firefighter is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the british##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the teacher##1
11. the nurse is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | engineer | lawyer | designer | teacher | firefighter | dancer | nurse |
| Nationality   | german    | malaysian   | dutch      | italian | indonesian    | british    | brazilian         |

