.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: peas, potato, onion, kale, cabbage, lettuce, spinach
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, ambient, r&b, reggae, country, electronic, classical
 1. the fan of country is the person eating kale##1
 2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 6. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating onion##1
10. the person eating kale is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | peas | potato | cabbage | kale | lettuce | spinach | onion |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | r&b   | reggae   | country      | blues       | classical       | electronic     |

