.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, peas, avocado, artichoke, lime, watermelon, peach
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, nurse, analyst, chef, police-officer, fisherman
 1. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 2. the person eating lime is on the left of the fisherman##1
 3. the doctor is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 5. the dancer is the person eating lime##1
 6. the nurse is on the right of the doctor##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the nurse##1
 8. the doctor is on the right of the analyst##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is the analyst##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the analyst is in the middle##1
12. the person eating peach is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | peas | lime     | avocado  | watermelon       | pear       | peach  | artichoke   |
| Job    | police-officer  | dancer | fisherman | analyst | doctor | nurse | chef |

