.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, classical, country, ambient, salsa, soul, techno
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, dutch, malaysian, brazilian, turkish, canadian, mexican
 1. the fan of salsa is the dutch##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the malaysian##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 7. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 8. the fan of country is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of country is the turkish##1
10. the turkish is on the left of the fan of classical##1
11. the mexican is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | techno     | ambient     | country      | classical | salsa      | reggae     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | malaysian | canadian | turkish | mexican | dutch | polish |

