.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: mouseing, rock-climbing, camping, collecting, dancing, baking, reading
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, cat, hamster, turtle, pony, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | camping | baking     | collecting | reading | dancing | mouseing |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | turtle | pony     | chinchilla         | hamster     | mouse        |

