.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, mirinda, milk, cola, hot-chocolate, tea
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, car, motorbike, snowmobile, subway, airplane
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | hot-chocolate   | lemonade | milk | tea  | cola | water |
| Transport   | motorbike   | snowmobile | scooter | subway     | taxi | airplane | car   |

