.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, sports, disaster, thriller, family, spy
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, bike, subway, helicopter, airplane, scooter, van
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the bus is the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | spy | disaster | thriller | family     | superhero | sports |
| Transport     | scooter | helicopter      | van | subway    | airplane | bike   | bus  |

